ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does the crypto swapping process work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app facilitates seamless crypto swapping by connecting to various decentralized exchanges and finding the best rates. Simply select the cryptocurrencies you want to swap, enter the amount, and confirm the transaction. The process is quick, secure, and user-friendly.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: We support a wide range of popular cryptocurrencies, including Bitcoin, Ethereum, and many altcoins. The list of available tokens is constantly expanding to provide you with more options for your swapping needs.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Are there any fees for using the app?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: While we don't charge any additional fees for using our app, there are network fees associated with blockchain transactions. These fees vary depending on the cryptocurrencies involved and network congestion. We always display the estimated fees before you confirm your swap.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: We take your privacy and security seriously. Our app operates on a non-custodial basis, meaning we never hold your funds or private keys. We also employ industry-standard encryption and security measures to protect any personal information you provide.

FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common questions about our crypto swapping app
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app supports a wide range of popular cryptocurrencies, including Bitcoin, Ethereum, and many altcoins. Check the app for the full list of supported coins.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: How long does a swap take?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Most swaps are completed within minutes. However, the exact time can vary depending on network congestion and the specific cryptocurrencies involved.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Are there any fees for swapping?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Yes, there are small fees associated with each swap. These include network fees and a small service fee. The exact amount will be displayed before you confirm your swap.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Is my crypto safe when using the app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: We prioritize security and use industry-standard encryption and safety measures. However, always ensure you're using official app links and never share your private keys.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Do I need to create an account to use the app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: No, our app doesn't require account creation. You can start swapping crypto immediately by connecting your wallet or entering your receiving address.
